		(property "Description" "Generic (polarity unspecified). iseg APS series programmable DC-HV converter module, 7-pin, 39.6 x 15.7 x 11 mm. Vset 0..Vref -> |Vout| 0..Vnom. /ON is active low (LOW or n.c. = HV ON). WARNING: output is NOT internally limited -- Vset above Vref drives |Vout| above Vnom; VSET has an internal 10k pull-up to Vref, so an OPEN VSET NODE COMMANDS FULL SCALE."
